      <div class="hard"></div>

      <div>
        <h1 class="text">Luminous People</h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Talking to you makes me aim for many things,<br>For example, to love roses more,<br>To let the thorns go by.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">To turn sadness into a halo of light,<br>To transform energy with great restlessness.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">To gaze at the Moon, with a voice of survival,<br>Awakening the wolf I carry inside.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Overcoming absences with your company,<br>Reciting Neruda’s verses,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Collecting stones without meaning to,<br>Until creating buildings with a brush.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I receive your words like someone<br>Who drinks water in an immense desert,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">And naked I dive into an unexplored river,<br>Emerging new and triumphant once more.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">With your presence by my side, I begin to open doors,<br>It helps me find the key to my most<br>precious chest, having you close</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I overcome anxiety, I sincerely receive<br>your advice, and I’m certain of<br>thinking less and acting more.</p>
      </div>

